data.description: Discover the perfect blend of affordability and comfort with this charming 3 bed 2 bath move-in ready single-level home in Madras, Oregon.   This comfortable residence is not only cute and clean but also boasts numerous features that make it an excellent choice for your new home. Key Features: spacious open floor plan w/ vaulted ceilings, large kitchen complete with tile countertops, recessed lighting, and a refrigerator included, attached 2-Car Garage w/ ample storage space, newer flooring, low-maintenance zero landscaping, peaceful and private back deck, walking distance to the Madras Bike and Skate Park, ideal for active individuals and families.  This Madras home is not only affordable but also ready for you to move in and start making cherished memories. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own this wonderful property.  Contact your favorite realtor to arrange a private tour of this great home.
